cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with generating image captions. It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it focuses on generating Japanese captions. Machine learning (cs.LG) is also relevant as the paper discusses the use of neural networks for caption generation. Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with automated caption generation. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also a possibility as the paper involves constructing a large-scale dataset.
